        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "As we have already said, so now I say again: If anybody is preaching to you a gospel other than what you accepted, let them be under God’s curse!"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "I say again what we have said before: If anyone preaches any other Good News than the one you welcomed, let that person be cursed."
      }
